data.title: What's the dark side of Sweden?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 114): Here it goes the dark side of Sweden. I must note there are a ton of things I like and love about Sweden. However I feel the need to bring up its dark side.

1 It is pitch black dark as night during winter. Some places get 24 hours of darkness in the north. It is a literal nigh...
